610
00:18:43,099 --> 00:18:45,259
That's my coffin money!

611
00:18:45,579 --> 00:18:48,200
Why don't you call and ask?

612
00:18:48,579 --> 00:18:49,299
Don't panic.

613
00:18:49,299 --> 00:18:51,099
I'll call.

614
00:18:51,900 --> 00:18:52,500
Okay, I know.

615
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:53,299
I know.

616
