680
00:20:55,339 --> 00:20:56,819
Xiao Cai, you must be strong.

681
00:20:56,819 --> 00:20:58,220
You must not faint.

682
00:20:58,500 --> 00:21:00,220
You have to believe in the distance!

683
00:21:00,980 --> 00:21:02,059
Here.

684
00:21:02,059 --> 00:21:02,480
Find...

685
