706
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:51,480
Don't harbor any...

707
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:52,960
...illusions of slipping through.

708
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:54,099
What th...

709
00:21:54,099 --> 00:21:55,059
Wha...

710
00:21:55,059 --> 00:21:55,839
What is this?

711
00:21:56,039 --> 00:21:57,000
